{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","title":"progress","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known and when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/progr